#  Business Insights

##  High Demand - Low Stock

Some products have demand greater than available stock → risk of stockouts.

 Action: Increase reorder frequency

---

##  Low Inventory Turnover

Certain products are not selling fast → capital is blocked.

 Action: Discount or remove slow-moving products

---

##  Supplier Risk

Suppliers with:

* High lead time
* Low reliability
Action: Replace or diversify suppliers

---

##  Warehouse Imbalance

Some warehouses handle more stock than others.

 Action: Redistribute inventory

---

## Sales Trend Insight

Monthly trends show fluctuations → possible seasonality.

 Action: Plan inventory based on demand cycles
